                    <h3><i>Junior Kindy</i></h3>
                    <p>Our Junior Kindy room provides a vibrant, engaging room full of wonderful learning opportunities. Children from 2 ½ - 3 ½ years old enjoy the home corner, literacy table and maths shelf where they can self-select and explore concepts supported by talented and highly experienced Educators.</p>
