                <td>
                    <h3><i>Kindergarten</i></h3>
                    <p>Our Kindy room is an integrated Department for Education approved Preschool which provides the flexibility to utilise the long day care hours. There is a reduced preschool fee (Universal Access) that is available within specific times for children to access in the year before starting school. The kindy programme is designed to incorporate children’s interests and strengths and follows the Australian Early Years Framework.</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>
                        <a href="~/Content/RoomHandBooks/Kindy handbook 2018 -ReDesign.pdf" target="_blank">Click here for the handbook</a>
                    </p>
                </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td>
                    <h3><i>Nursery</i></h3>
                    <p>Our Nursery room offers education and care for children aged from 2 years to 3 years old. Nursery provides an extension from Babies with a very stimulating and engaging curriculum. The children engage in ‘hands-on’ experiences and explore their world around them. They have an extra play space which provides an outdoor undercover area especially great for those wet weather days for active toddlers.</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>
                        <a href="~/Content/RoomHandBooks/Child Care booklet -ReDesign.pdf" target="_blank">Click here for the handbook</a>
                    </p>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <h3><i>Babyroom</i></h3>
                    <p>You will receive a very warm welcome when you step into our Baby Room. With a maximum of only 8 babies, the environment is a calm and nurturing space that provides high quality care and education to babies from 6 weeks up to 2 years of age. The two permanent Educators are very experienced with supporting both children and families to settle in and begin building secure relationships.</p>
                    <br />
                    <p>
                        <a href="~/Content/RoomHandBooks/Baby_Room_Handbook.pdf" target="_blank">Click here for the handbook</a>
                    </p>
